divs: Sighting DetailsI was standing in my backyard and saw two orange lights. I noticed them after looking up to see what was making noise in the tree. (It was a squirrel). They were about one hundred yards apart and I would estimate 1,000 ft. above the ground. I could not see waht was between them but it was darker than the rest of the sky so I assume thre was something there. They moved across the sky silently from the N.W. to the S.E. right over my house. They disappeared about three blocks from my house. I felt very nervous after i saw this but eventually calmed down and felt a kind of content feeling.
Summary: Strange lights moving across the sky.
